Yes.

298
00:13:42,160 --> 00:13:43,080
And guess what?

299
00:13:45,960 --> 00:13:48,620
I guess you actually learned something from me.

300
00:13:48,960 --> 00:13:49,560
Come here.

301
00:13:55,320 --> 00:13:56,180
This is the guy.

302
00:13:56,720 --> 00:13:57,960
He's been very suspicious lately,

303
