304
00:13:59,880 --> 00:14:00,340
Zoom in.

305
00:14:00,640 --> 00:14:01,440
Zoom in on him.

306
00:14:01,880 --> 00:14:02,040
Yun = Li Chuan.

307
00:14:02,040 --> 00:14:02,920
The neck area.

308
00:14:02,920 --> 00:14:03,320
Li Jiu.

309
00:14:06,560 --> 00:14:08,000
What, do you guys know him?

310
00:14:08,000 --> 00:14:08,930
I don't know him.

311
00:14:09,880 --> 00:14:10,480
Oh, right.

312
00:14:10,800 --> 00:14:11,960
The Buddha statue transport route

313
