315
00:14:16,880 --> 00:14:17,480
Thank you.

316
00:14:58,160 --> 00:14:58,960
Guannan.

317
00:15:20,080 --> 00:15:20,610
Guannan.

318
00:15:22,520 --> 00:15:23,450
Don't follow me.

319
00:15:24,120 --> 00:15:24,650
Guannan.

320
00:15:35,040 --> 00:15:36,240
I never, ever

321
00:15:36,240 --> 00:15:37,640
